rComments: Probably one of the best profs at UofT. He is extremely passionate about his work, which greatly reflects in his lectures. I looked forward to the lectures every week. His exam is brutal, but you can get good marks on the essays if you do what he asks.  He's a difficult prof, but his lectures make up for it.
